Title: Lysol healthy touch hand soap refill(255 ml)
Description: LYSOL healthy touch no-touch hand soap system helps eliminate the millions of germs that your hands can pick up each day. Propylene glycol is a small organic alcohol commonly used as a skin conditioning agent. It has been associated with irritant and allergic contact dermatitis as well as contact urticaria in humans. METHYLISOTHIAZOLINONE (aka ISOTHIAZOLONE and abbreviated with a number), is a widely-used preservative; has been associated with allergies and immunotoxicity.
